.guitar-quest-piece.container
  .panel.panel-default
    .panel-heading 20 points
    .panel-body
      h4 Estudio Sin Luz
      p Andres Segovia
      .row.actions
        .col-md-4
          iframe(
            src="https://embed.spotify.com/?uri=spotify:track:1gFOPRH492kvYMN19xnMoJ"
            width="100%"
            height="80"
            frameborder="0"
            allowtransparency="true"
          )
        .col-md-4
          a.link-btn.btn.btn-default.btn-block(href='http://imslp.org/wiki/Fantasie,_Op.7_(Sor,_Fernando)' target="_blank")
            div
              i.fa.fa-book.fa-3x
            div Get Sheet Music
        .col-md-4
          .link-btn.btn.btn-default.btn-block
            div
              i.fa.fa-video-camera.fa-3x
            div Request Video Lesson

      .row
        .col-xs-12
          p Meh bespoke Odd Future, sriracha YOLO Pinterest twee +1 semiotics mumblecore XOXO put a bird on it DIY mixtape. Marfa narwhal fap, flexitarian Williamsburg beard gentrify Austin kale chips swag American Apparel cold-pressed freegan. Flannel Truffaut cray cold-pressed. Crucifix stumptown quinoa, mixtape Truffaut four loko McSweeney's pour-over tofu flannel gentrify Wes Anderson chambray beard cardigan. Post-ironic heirloom master cleanse, slow-carb pickled iPhone chambray quinoa narwhal VHS Wes Anderson.

      p To complete upload a video of you playing the piece below. The piece should be memorized, played with good technique, and played musically.

      .row.well.video-well
        .col-xs-12.text-center
          .select-video(ng-hide='pieceCtrl.videoSelected' ngf-select ngf-change="pieceCtrl.upload($file)")
            div
              i.fa.fa-upload.fa-5x
            h5 Select video to submit
          .loading.row.text-center(ng-show='pieceCtrl.videoSelected && !pieceCtrl.videoUploadSrc')
            h5 Uploading...
            .col-xs-8.col-xs-offset-2
              progressbar(
                max="100"
                value="pieceCtrl.progressPercentage"
              )
          .submission-successful.text-center(ng-show='pieceCtrl.videoUploadSrc')
            video.video-preview(controls)
            a(href='#') Submit a different video
